extends layout.pug

block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div

      //- Projects Title.
      h1 My Projects

      //-Project descriptions
      p.lead.text-light
        | These are some of the apps that I have created, most are using JavaSript, there are links to the GitHub repoistories, as well as live links to the apps. 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3

      each item, index in projects
        .cell
          a(href=`/projects/${item.id}`)
            img.thumbnail(src=`${item.img_urls[0]}`)
            h5 #{item.project_name}